rComments: Good, interesting class...helpful with any questions

The ideal for what a young college professor should be.  Everything is broken down and test are generally straight forward.  I would take another class even if I didn't need it just to have him again.

Ryan was a great professor. He never kept us in lecture longer than we had to be there and would always let us out early. He gave us study guides for the tests, but actually made the tests so we were forced to read the chapters and study. He was a very good teacher, and had all of the lecture notes online.
